sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as Клиент
    participant UI as React Frontend
    participant OrderController as OrderController
    participant OrderService as OrderService
    participant ProductRepo as ProductRepository
    participant OrderRepo as OrderRepository
    participant DB as Database
    Client->>UI: Добавляет товар в корзину
    Client->>UI: Нажимает Оформить заказ
    UI->>OrderController: POST /api/orders
    OrderController->>OrderService: createOrder(request, user)
    OrderService->>ProductRepo: Проверить остатки товаров
    ProductRepo->>DB: SELECT products
    DB-->>ProductRepo: Данные товаров
    OrderService->>OrderRepo: Сохранить заказ и позиции
    OrderRepo->>DB: INSERT orders, order_items
    DB-->>OrderRepo: Заказ создан
    OrderService-->>OrderController: OrderDto
    OrderController-->>UI: 201 Created
    UI-->>Client: Заказ успешно оформлен
